<inglise> Article 11 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 11 </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall supply the Statistical Office of the European Communities with any information it may require of them regarding the organization and methodology of the surveys covered by this Regulation; in particular, they shall provide detailes of the timetable for the data collection operations in the field. </inglise>
<eesti> Liikmesriigid edastavad Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Statistikaametile kogu teabe, mida viimane v&otilde;ib vajada k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega h&otilde;lmatud uuringute korraldamiseks ja metoodika v&auml;ljat&ouml;&ouml;tamiseks; eelk&otilde;ige esitavad nad &uuml;ksikasjad kohapealse andmekogumise ajakava kohta. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 12 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 12 </eesti>
<inglise> In the context of the Eurofarm project, the Statistical Office of the European Communities shall be responsible for disseminating the tabular results of the survey. </inglise>
